{{ persona }}

---
Create a LinkedIn carousel post from insights gathered at {{ conference_name }}{% if conference_date %} ({{ conference_date }}){% endif %}.

SYNTHESIS:
{{ conference_summary }}

Suggested hook: {{ best_hook }}

Themes:
{% for theme in themes %}
{{ loop.index }}. {{ theme.title }} [{{ theme.novelty }}]: {{ theme.insight }}
   Evidence: {{ (theme.evidence or []) | join(' | ') }}
{% endfor %}

Hot Takes:
{% if hot_takes %}
{% for ht in hot_takes %}
🔥 {{ ht.claim }} [{{ ht.source }}] — {{ ht.why_surprising }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
None — use the most counterintuitive theme as the hook.
{% endif %}

Top Quotes:
{% for q in top_quotes[:3] %}
- {{ q }}
{% endfor %}

Top Data Points:
{% for dp in top_data_points[:3] %}
- {{ dp }}
{% endfor %}

---
CAROUSEL REQUIREMENTS:
- 8–12 slides total
- Mix slide types: title, content (insights), stat (data points), quote (speaker quotes), cta
- Each slide: under 50 words of visible text — people swipe fast
- Slide headlines must be specific and punchy — no vague headers like "Key Insights"
- Content slides: max 3 bullets, each under 15 words
- Final slide: clear CTA + follow prompt

For EVERY content/stat/quote slide include an `image_prompt`: one-sentence DALL-E prompt for a supporting background or accent graphic.
Style rules for image prompts: dark background (#0D1117), LinkedIn blue accents, professional, abstract/data-viz aesthetic, NO text in the generated image.

Also generate:
- A `caption`: 100–150 word LinkedIn post text to accompany the carousel (hook + context + swipe prompt)
- `hashtags`: best hashtag string for this content

---
Return ONLY valid JSON — no markdown fences, no preamble. Exact format:

{
  "slides": [
    {
      "type": "title",
      "headline": "...",
      "subtitle": "{{ conference_name }}, {{ conference_date }}",
      "visual_note": "description of ideal background visual"
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "slide_number": 1,
      "headline": "...",
      "bullets": ["...", "...", "..."],
      "visual_note": "...",
      "image_prompt": "DALL-E prompt for supporting visual..."
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "slide_number": 2,
      "stat": "73%",
      "context": "...",
      "source": "Speaker Name, Company",
      "visual_note": "...",
      "image_prompt": "..."
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "slide_number": 3,
      "quote": "...",
